Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,547)}Neo Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(624,538)}Ultimate Photon Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IV, are you ready for your punishment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Photon Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma won!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... For me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to lose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto... Where is Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just ask your rotten souls {\i1}directly{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't retrieve their Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're protected by these crests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you back the pain you gave us double!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Haruto back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both... disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto is right up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will grant Haruto-{\i0}sama{\i1}'s wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, hold up a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How dare you... How dare you trick-\N - Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did... What did you do to Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry. He is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he used up all of his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he gave the remainder of his power to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time I'll protect my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... I did this to Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo... You are Kazuma-{\i1}san{\i0}'s son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How do you know my dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(525,510)}"Number 44: The Forked Paths of Destiny!\N Yuma Abandons Dueling!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... might still be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean by that?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad... My dad's alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean that my father is in the Astral World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,515)}Hey... Astral World's the place you come from, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(651,518)}Why would my dad be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(658,522)}I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if we collect the Numbers and get your memories back... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto... He's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito, you're a pitiful soldier working for Haruto's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save my brother, I sold my soul to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto... won't recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Haruto gets better...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mission is to destroy the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if my dad's really in Astral World...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! My dad might still be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mood ain't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No can do. You can't take a single step beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you guys do whatever you like with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stand by Haruto's side, you can't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice but to leave this to Mr. Heartland for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, why didn't you tell us that Yuma Tsukumo was working with the Original Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one hunting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny you should say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got along well during that Tag Duel, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a nice mood going and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who will defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone holding a Number is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stand before me as a hindrance, I'll consider you my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto! Oh, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm responsible for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grief and sadness is much appreciated, Faker-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Heartland, who stole Haruto's power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Kaito's report, it was the doing of a group of people wielding special crests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crests?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people will eventually show themselves again during the Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Let's take those people apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we will take Haruto's power back from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no choice but to go to Astral World and find my dad with my own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care about the Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I don't care about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Dad... Dad might be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, for now I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, you'll have to cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that getup of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not running away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, don't get too surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to say Dad might still be alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from Kotori-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're trying to find Dad and bring him home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a true blue fool, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad said he found the top of the world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go to the top of the world and find Dad there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the top of the world or the Astral World, I'm definitely gonna find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, what about the Duel Carnival?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been some time, wouldn't ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Rokujuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, are you... abandoning Dueling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard my cute little disciple was trying his best and standing up challenge after challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to leave the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no idea such a thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, wanna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Gramps, but I don't really feel like Dueling right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not abandon Dueling that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on leaving, you'll do it only after defeating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize Yuma, but I'm not going to help you out during this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll be able to handle this all on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto's power is beginning to awaken inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Gagaga Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah! Now I've got five Monsters on my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps only has one face-down Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn will decide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Girl, attack his face-down Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters were all... wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When fighting a match, you must {\i1}also{\i0} be sure to {\i1}notice{\i0} your opponent's set cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! But {\i1}I've {\i0}still got the advantage here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, then I guess it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Flip Summon Queen's Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Normal Summon King's Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King, Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When both Queen and King Knight are on the field, I can play the Jack card on the field from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Jack's Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Monsters all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a three-Monster-for-one combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here we have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Fusion Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse together the three royal knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Imperial Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the ultimate Fusion warrior, Arcana Knight Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3800 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tables have turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Arcana Knight Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Let's play another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in such a rush, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you are now, you couldn't even defeat {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you are now, you can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... I just don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I choose Astral or Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly decide something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned to use searching for your father as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning your rivals and your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned your family and even your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your partner must feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, look at your feet carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feet are strongly rooted in Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So use Dueling as your guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And take your first step from there toward your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is certain to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Dueling is the bond that connects you to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do love Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it's so difficult to gain control over it, even with the power of the crest in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faker, it's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow you all the way to the Parallel Universe with the very same power you desired!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait... Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, all I can do now is win in the Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win the Carnival, Mr. Heartland will gladly do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gramps. Who exactly is this Mr. Heartland guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Just as the name implies, he's Heartland's symbol and is quite popular with the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he's a symbol and that he's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an outer there's an inner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you find light, you're bound to find a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the best way to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Heartland... You could say the one hiding behind him is the mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one and only scientist called a genius in this decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's the mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man surrounded by mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be living right now or already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rumored that Dr. Faker was the one who created Heartland City.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Faker...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the last one to guide Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad and this man called Faker...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he's connected to Mr. Heartland, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I step toward him, my father might be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to ensure it, I need to continue winning in the Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yuma Tsukumo holds the Original Number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... Tsukumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Related to Kazuma Tsukumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the messenger from Astral World...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to put that card in, you don't need the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, will ya?! If I want it in, it's in! It's in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'd be better off replacing it with that Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one... Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, let's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.47,0:23:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of those countless flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They came at the expense of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me being able to reach those heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, even though I lost my way today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} Robin is participating in the Duel Carnival?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's up against Gauche of the Operation Committee!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:24:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dimensional ESPer Robin's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an awesome, awesome Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Robin and Gauche are intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Gauche's Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've seen that face before...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin hasn't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.92,0:24:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Nemesis Shows Up Late! Robin VS Gauche"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The WDC, lasting several days, is finally in its final day!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.73,0:24:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more Heart Piece and my set is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bringing it right to the tournament finals!
